{"text_id":90948,"tokens":["For"," many"," students",","," summer"," is"," a"," much","-","anticipated"," period"," of"," relaxation"," and"," rest","."," Yet"," it"," can"," also"," be"," a"," time"," that"," students"," fall"," behind"," on"," their"," studies"," due"," to"," a"," break"," in"," their"," learning","."," For"," this"," reason",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," consider"," ways"," to"," keep"," students"," engaged"," in"," learning"," through"," the"," summer"," months","."," One"," approach"," to"," this"," problem"," is"," for"," teachers"," to"," design"," and"," assign"," summer"," projects",","," and"," another"," option"," is"," for"," students"," to"," design"," their"," own"," summer"," projects",".","\n\n","In"," terms"," of"," teachers"," assigning"," summer"," projects",","," one"," advantage"," is"," that"," it"," would"," provide"," students"," with"," more"," structure"," and"," guidance"," throughout"," the"," summer","."," Students"," might"," find"," it"," easier"," to"," make"," progress"," on"," their"," studies"," when"," the"," expectations"," are"," outlined"," in"," advance","."," Furthermore",","," a"," teacher","-","driven"," approach"," might"," be"," beneficial"," to"," those"," students"," who"," have"," difficulty"," managing"," their"," own"," learning"," plan"," and"," need"," greater"," structure"," in"," order"," to"," succeed",".","\n\n","On"," the"," other"," hand",","," one"," potential"," downside"," to"," this"," approach"," is"," that"," it"," might"," create"," an"," added"," burden"," for"," teachers","."," Creating"," and"," managing"," summer"," projects"," is"," no"," small"," task",","," so"," if"," teachers"," were"," to"," assume"," this"," responsibility",","," it"," could"," add"," an"," unnecessary"," amount"," of"," work"," to"," their"," already"," busy"," workloads","."," It"," could"," also"," make"," it"," more"," difficult"," for"," teachers"," to"," take"," their"," own"," summer"," breaks"